ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Take this class. The way of looking at problems that is taught in this class is incredibly useful and is definitely something that you will use moving forward.

This course is an interesting and useful look into the field of model building. I would recommend it to anyone who is interested in learning more about models and some of the coding practices used to create useful models.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I will certainly be using the skills developed in this class for my research moving forward.
